I think you got the wrong `JSON response` when you call your API from the device. It can be an issue in your server. Let&#39;s say when you call your API using postman then you are getting your expected response like below(because your API call is ok)
```
{
&quot;status&quot;: 1,
&quot;message&quot;: &quot;Successful&quot;
}
```
And when you call you API from your application then you get the wrong `JSON response` from the server means API call is not ok [it can be happned due to many reasons].

```
&quot;{
&quot;status&quot;: 0,
&quot;message&quot;: &quot;&quot;
}&quot;
